OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry and chilly. Rain will
OL,7,Fspread from the southwest for a time
OL,8,Fovernight. Drier weather following on
OL,9,Fbehind later in the night.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FA dry and mostly cloudy day.
OL,12,FNorthern Moray and northern
OL,13,FAberdeenshire may see some hazy
OL,14,Fsunshine. Mild.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FCloudy
OL,17,Fand mild with patchy rain on
OL,18,FWednesday. Bright and breezy with
OL,19,Fscattered showers on Thursday, mainly
OL,20,Fdry in the east. Rain for a time on
OL,21,FFriday.
